{"tid":2408695,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梅根第二胎｜戴妃當年同日公佈懷有哈里 英作家讚賞今次公佈「帶來加州陽光」","createTime":"2021-02-15T07:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T10:52:14.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6d4e8026a4f9fa0cc4a4704ed326529134be68a2","tid":2408695,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T07:48:32.000Z","msg":"銳意經營形象 深諳「真正權力」在網上<br />\n英國《每日郵報》的專欄作家維恩（Sarah Vine）撰文讚賞哈里夫婦的喜訊，是為寒冷的英國帶來一絲加州陽光，形容照片中的兩人輕鬆愜意，「他們跟觀眾沒有視線接觸，就好像我們在窺視這個親密時刻，在最自然時刻的愛情寫照。這對愛侶互相凝視微笑，是如此專注，所有人所有事物都只是背景配襯。」<br />\n<br />\n維恩形容哈里夫婦這張照片風格優雅，有如荷李活大片電影海報，「他是內心受困擾的英俊王子，她是為他指路的美麗女演員，他們聯袂打破慣例，然後征服世界」。她讚又揚哈里夫婦深明現今世代「真正權力」不再落在「皇冠與皇宮」之中，而是互聯網與社交網站，如何定義一個人是視乎他們如何經營形象，「最終，他們領悟到了。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210215/SBH7OCBBYVBTNCSTC4YGX2CMG4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210215%2FSBH7OCBBYVBTNCSTC4YGX2CMG4%2F&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4efuvrtn4HlyTxFQ%2BxjLCx7s%3D&h=0c3dde5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210215%2FSBH7OCBBYVBTNCSTC4YGX2CMG4%2F&h=bb526afb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210215/SBH7OCBBYVBTNCSTC4YGX2CMG4/</a>"},{"pid":"9067d19274fb91d135786bf592a5d910fd6e61b9","tid":2408695,"uid":259901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T07:50:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而是互聯網與社交網站</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇錯，大把網民知道你隻死黑雞正臭閪，個朵臭到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d995281556438cc72ef6ba6f2c77cfdef32f2a","tid":2408695,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T07:57:07.000Z","msg":"相？"},{"pid":"8c530324d0c9b9472bd37d8021d56035ae007ff8","tid":2408695,"uid":238370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T10:46:49.000Z","msg":"哂到黑嗰隻陽光？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a